      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It can be difficult when you're surrounded by multiple enemies and you’re trying to put some distance between yourself and them. As I found out myself on multiple occasions, I often got stuck on buildings and took damage as the dash ability doesn’t quite give you enough distance when you use it.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "As for the pace, the gameplay is quite slow, which is to be expected because you’re controlling a massive monster and not a small agile human. However as previously mentioned, I wish the dash ability gave you a bit more distance, which would have sped up your escapes.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "My biggest issue is that there’s no online play which I would have just loved here. While there is local multiplayer available, it’s an option many sadly never use and online play helps to mitigate these issues.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
